about.summary: Monitoring filesystems events with inotify on Linux. http://github.com/seb-m/pyinotify/wiki

name: pyinotify
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.9.6" %}

package:
  name: pyinotify
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pyinotify/pyinotify-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 9c998a5d7606ca835065cdabc013ae6c66eb9ea76a00a1e3bc6e0cfe2b4f71f4

build:
  number: 1000
  skip: True  # [not linux]
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv"

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pyinotify

about:
  home: http://github.com/seb-m/pyinotify
  license: MIT
  license_file: COPYING
  summary: Monitoring filesystems events with inotify on Linux. http://github.com/seb-m/pyinotify/wiki

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kwilcox
